# llms.txt — tokenprice.fyi
# https://llmstxt.org/

# tokenprice.fyi is an independent price record of AI model APIs.
# It tracks prices across seven categories — language, embeddings, rerank,
# speech-to-text, text-to-speech, image generation, and video generation.
# Language models carry full per-token price history, updated daily; the other
# categories are dated, sourced list prices in each API's native billing unit.

> tokenprice.fyi: the price record of AI model APIs. Per-token rates with full history for language models (Claude, GPT, Gemini, Grok, DeepSeek), plus dated, sourced list prices for embeddings, rerank, speech, image, and video models.

